AIOHTTP OAuth Client
####################

.. _description:

AIOHTTP OAuth Client -- OAuth support for Aiohttp/Asyncio.

.. _badges:

.. image:: http://img.shields.io/travis/klen/aioauth-client.svg?style=flat-square
    :target: http://travis-ci.org/klen/aioauth-client
